\CommentTok{#first write some functions that help automate the process}
\CommentTok{##########}
\CommentTok{#this gets the average FPKM for a given line from the sc_des matrix}
\NormalTok{getAvgFPKM.MAnew <-}\StringTok{ }\ControlFlowTok{function}\NormalTok{(line) \{ }\CommentTok{#for line as "###" string}
\NormalTok{  r1 <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{paste}\NormalTok{(}\KeywordTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"X"}\NormalTok{,line,}\StringTok{"_0"}\NormalTok{),}\DataTypeTok{collapse=}\StringTok{""}\NormalTok{) }\CommentTok{#triplicates are named X[LINE]_[rep]}
\NormalTok{  r2 <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{paste}\NormalTok{(}\KeywordTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"X"}\NormalTok{,line,}\StringTok{"_1"}\NormalTok{),}\DataTypeTok{collapse=}\StringTok{""}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{  r3 <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{paste}\NormalTok{(}\KeywordTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"X"}\NormalTok{,line,}\StringTok{"_2"}\NormalTok{),}\DataTypeTok{collapse=}\StringTok{""}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{  reps <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{sc_des.MAnew[,}\KeywordTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"locus"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"tracking_id"}\NormalTok{,r1,r2,r3)] }\CommentTok{#get those 4 columns out of the descendant dataset}
\NormalTok{  reps[reps}\OperatorTok{==}\DecValTok{0}\NormalTok{] <-}\StringTok{ }\OtherTok{NA} \CommentTok{#replace 0 values with NA as before}
\NormalTok{  desAvg.MA <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{rowMeans}\NormalTok{(reps[,}\KeywordTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\OperatorTok{-}\DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{,}\OperatorTok{-}\DecValTok{2}\NormalTok{)],}\DataTypeTok{na.rm=}\NormalTok{T)}
\NormalTok{  desAvg.MA <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{cbind}\NormalTok{(sc_des.MAnew[,}\KeywordTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{,}\DecValTok{2}\NormalTok{)],desAvg.MA)}
  \CommentTok{#colnames(desAvg) <- c("chr","gene",paste(c(line,"_Avg"),collapse=""))}
  \KeywordTok{return}\NormalTok{(desAvg.MA) }\CommentTok{#returned is a matrix equivalent to ancAvg: chrm, gene, and line average FPKM }
\NormalTok{\}}
